Basic Knowledge about VAG Diagnostic Tool<br/><br/>An abundant of auto diagnostic tools have been developed to   detect, check and repair all controlling units of vehicles. As to VAG   Diagnostic Tool, it is the emphasis that I introduce today.<a href="http://en.pan.netcom/go/out/url=-aHR0cDovL3d3dy5yZWxpYWJsZXRvcC5jb20vU3VwcGx5LXZhZy1kaWFnbm9zdGljLXRvb2xfYzEx" target="_blank">VAG Diagnostic Tool</a>is capable of reprogramming central locks or Radio, diagnosing a   problem with the ABS, Airbags, or Automatic Transmission, recalibrating   Immobilizer after swapping ECU’s, resetting Service Reminder Indicators,   and communicating with pre-1996 model (not OBD-II compliant) vehicles.&lt;/p&gt;
